AI Resume Analyzer

An AI-powered Resume Screening and Ranking System built using Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Machine Learning techniques. This application helps recruiters efficiently shortlist candidates and allows job seekers to evaluate and improve their resumes based on job descriptions.

Overview

The system analyzes resumes against a given job description and computes a match score using a combination of TF-IDF and BERT-based semantic similarity. It also identifies matched and missing skills and generates recruiter-style feedback to provide meaningful insights.

Features

- Resume ranking based on job description
- Semantic similarity using Sentence Transformers (BERT)
- Keyword matching using TF-IDF
- Identification of matched and missing skills
- Human-readable recruiter-style feedback
- Candidate ATS score evaluation
- Support for multiple file formats (PDF, DOCX, TXT)
- Separate modes for recruiter and candidate usage
- Web interface built with Flask

Tech Stack

Backend:
- Python
- Flask

Machine Learning and NLP:
- Scikit-learn (TF-IDF, similarity)
- Sentence Transformers (BERT)
- spaCy (text preprocessing)

File Processing:
- PyPDF2
- python-docx

Frontend:
- HTML
- CSS

