Installation and Setup

1. Clone the repository:
   git clone https://github.com/vaibhavibtech2023-dev/resume-analyzer.git
   cd resume-analyzer

2. Create a virtual environment:
   python -m venv venv
   venv\Scripts\activate      (Windows)
   source venv/bin/activate   (Mac/Linux)

3. Install dependencies:
   pip install -r requirements.txt

4. Install spaCy model:
   python -m spacy download en_core_web_sm

5. Run the application:
   python main.py

6. Open in browser:
   http://127.0.0.1:5000

Usage

Recruiter Mode:
Upload multiple resumes and provide a job description to receive ranked candidates along with insights and scores.

Candidate Mode:
Upload a single resume and job description to receive an ATS-style evaluation, including strengths and areas for improvement.

Deployment

The application can be deployed using platforms such as Render, Railway, or PythonAnywhere.

Future Enhancements

